1.Auth0 l\'e0 g\'ec?\b0\fs22\par
Auth0 v\f2\lang1066\u7873? c\f1\u417? b\f2\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t n\u7873?n t\u7843?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\lang1066\u7911?y quy\u7873?n cho \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a b\u7841?n. N\f0\lang1033\'f3 cung c\f2\lang1066\u7845?p t\u7845?t c\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'f4ng c\f2\lang1066\u7909? c\u7847?n thi\u7871?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f2\lang1066\u7921?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ch\f2\lang1066\u7841?y c\f1\u417? s\f2\u7903? h\u7841? t\u7847?ng nh\u7853?n d\u7841?ng an to\f0\lang1033\'e0n bao g\f2\lang1066\u7891?m x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c, b\u7843?o v\u7879? d\u7919? li\u7879?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 qu\f2\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd m\f2\lang1066\u7853?t kh\u7849?u.\par
Auth0 c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? tri\u7875?n khai \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p m\u7897?t l\u7847?n (SSO), kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f2\lang1066\u7847?n m\u7853?t kh\u7849?u, x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889?, v.v. N\f0\lang1033\'f3 cung c\f2\lang1066\u7845?p m\u7897?t API \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f2\lang1066\u7875?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng Auth0 trong c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a ri\f0\lang1033\'eang h\f2\lang1066\u7885? \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? cung c\u7845?p x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a h\u7885?. C\f0\lang1033\'f3 nhi\f2\lang1066\u7873?u l\f0\lang1033\'fd do \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? ch\u7885?n Auth0 l\f0\lang1033\'e0m n\f2\lang1066\u7873?n t\u7843?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c, ch\u7859?ng h\u7841?n nh\f1\u432?\par
