\f0\fs32\lang1033 2.\f2\lang1066 T\f0\lang1033\'ednh n\f1\'e3ng Auth0\b0\fs22\par
H\f0\'e0ng t\f2\lang1066\u7927? ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0ang \'f0\'e3ng k\f0\'fd ho\f2\lang1066\u7863?c \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng web \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? ch\u7885?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1c d\f2\lang1066\u7883?ch v\u7909? c\u7911?a b\u7841?n. H\u7885? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0ang \'f0\f2\u7863?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ho\f2\lang1066\u7863?c th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh mua. Vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f2\lang1066\u7921?ng m\u7897?t quy tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c b\u7843?o m\u7853?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\f2\lang1066\u7847?n thi\u7871?t cho b\u7845?t k\u7923? lu\u7891?ng ho\u7841?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7897?ng n\f0\lang1033\'e0o nh\f1\u432? v\f2\lang1066\u7853?y.\par
Auth0 c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? h\u7895? tr\u7907? chu\u7849?n b\u7883? \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c b\u7843?o m\u7853?t t\u7889?t nh\u7845?t. N\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'f3 nhi\f2\lang1066\u7873?u t\f0\lang1033\'ednh n\f1\'e3ng l\f0\'e0m cho n\'f3 tr\f2\lang1066\u7903? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t l\u7921?a ch\u7885?n tuy\u7879?t v\u7901?i cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f2\lang1066\u7875?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng. M\u7897?t s\u7889? t\f0\lang1033\'ednh n\f1\'e3ng l\f0\'e0:\par
\tab\b\f1\'d0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p chung\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\f2\lang1066 D\u7845?u hi\u7879?u duy nh\u7845?t tr\f0\lang1033\'ean\par
\tab X\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889?\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\f2\lang1066 Kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f3 m\f2\lang1066\u7853?t kh\u7849?u\par
\b0 Auth0 cung c\u7845?p ho\u7841?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7897?ng \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p truy\u7873?n th\u7889?ng th\f0\lang1033\'fac \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7849?y tr\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng. N\'f3 cho ph\'e9p ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c nh\u7845?t qu\f0\lang1033\'e1n v\'e0 c\f2\lang1066\u7843?nh b\f0\lang1033\'e1o h\f2\lang1066\u7885? v\u7873? n\u7895? l\u7921?c l\u7915?a \f1\'f0\f2\u7843?o. Thi\u7871?t k\u7871? \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p ph\u7893? bi\u7871?n khi\u7871?n ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng ch\f2\lang1066\u7881? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t bi\u7875?u m\u7851?u cho th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p. N\u7871?u c\f0\lang1033\'f3 b\f2\lang1066\u7845?t c\u7913? \f1\'f0i\f2\u7873?u g\f0\lang1033\'ec \f1\'f0\f0\'e1ng ng\f2\lang1066\u7901?, n\f0\lang1033\'f3 s\f2\lang1066\u7869? b\u7883? t\u7915? ch\u7889?i.\par
B\u7845?t c\u7913? khi n\f0\lang1033\'e0o ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p, h\u7885? s\u7869? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c chuy\u7875?n h\f1\u432?\f2\u7899?ng \f1\'f0\f2\u7871?n m\f0\lang1033\'e1y ch\f2\lang1066\u7911? chung \f1\'f0\f2\u7841?i di\u7879?n cho h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f2\lang1066\u7913?c \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p c\u7911?a doanh nghi\u7879?p b\u7841?n. T\u7845?t c\u7843? qu\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\'ecnh \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p c\f1\u361?ng nh\u432? x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c di\u7877?n ra c\f0\lang1033\'f9ng m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t l\f0\lang1033\'fac, \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7843?m b\u7843?o t\f0\lang1033\'ednh b\f2\lang1066\u7843?o m\u7853?t.\par
\b\fs28 D\u7845?u hi\u7879?u duy nh\u7845?t tr\f0\lang1033\'ean\b0\fs22\par
\f1\'d0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p m\u7897?t l\u7847?n cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\'f3 quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n truy c\u7853?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\f2\lang1066\u7845?t c\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng m\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\f2\lang1066\u7885? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\'f4ng qua th\'f4ng tin \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p duy nh\u7845?t. V\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f2\lang1066\u7909?; b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng t\f0\lang1033\'e0i kho\f2\lang1066\u7843?n Google c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng d\u7883?ch v\u7909?. Tuy nhi\f0\lang1033\'ean, vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f2\lang1066\u7921?ng m\u7897?t \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p duy nh\u7845?t c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? v\u7915?a t\u7889?n th\u7901?i gian v\u7915?a t\u7889?n k\f0\lang1033\'e9m.\par
Tuy nhi\'ean, vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c tri\u7875?n khai \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p m\u7897?t l\u7847?n qua Auth0 c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m n\'ean \f1\'f0i\f2\lang1066\u7873?u k\u7923? di\u7879?u trong th\u7901?i gian ng\u7855?n h\f1\u417?n. N\f0\lang1033\'f3 h\f2\lang1066\u7895? tr\u7907? h\f1\u417?n 40 nh\f0\lang1033\'e0 cung c\f2\lang1066\u7845?p danh t\f0\lang1033\'ednh. B\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? t\f1\'e3ng t\f2\u7927? l\u7879? chuy\u7875?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i b\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch li\'ean k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t c\f0\lang1033\'e1c t\'e0i kho\f2\lang1066\u7843?n tr\f0\lang1033\'ean nhi\f2\lang1066\u7873?u n\u7873?n t\u7843?ng. Cung c\u7845?p s\u7921? t\u7921? do \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? vi\u7871?t m\f0\lang1033\'e3 m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t l\u7847?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\'edch h\f2\lang1066\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t n\u7889?i kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c nhau.\par
\b\fs28 X\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889?:\b0\fs22\par
X\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889? l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t lo\u7841?i x\f0\lang1033\'e1c minh y\'eau c\f2\lang1066\u7847?u nhi\u7873?u h\f1\u417?n m\f2\u7897?t lo\u7841?i th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?n d\u7841?ng. \f1\'d0i\f2\u7873?u n\f0\lang1033\'e0y l\'e0m t\f1\'e3ng t\f0\'ednh b\f2\lang1066\u7843?o m\u7853?t c\u7911?a \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng, gi\u7843?m nguy c\f1\u417? b\f2\u7883? truy c\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'e1i ph\'e9p. Lo\f2\lang1066\u7841?i th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin bao g\f2\lang1066\u7891?m;\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\b\f2\lang1066 Ki\u7871?n th\u7913?c: th\u7913? m\f0\lang1033\'e0 ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng bi\f2\lang1066\u7871?t (m\u7853?t kh\u7849?u)\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\f2\lang1066 S\u7903? h\u7919?u: th\u7913? m\f0\lang1033\'e0 ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\f0\'e3 c\'f3 (thi\f2\lang1066\u7871?t b\u7883? di \f1\'f0\f2\u7897?ng)\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\f2\lang1066 T\f0\lang1033\'ednh k\f2\lang1066\u7871? th\u7915?a: th\u7913? gi\f0\lang1033\'fap ph\'e2n bi\f2\lang1066\u7879?t ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng (qu\'e9t v\'e2n tay ho\f2\lang1066\u7863?c v\f0\lang1033\'f5ng m\f2\lang1066\u7841?c)\par
\f0\lang1033\tab\f2\lang1066 Auth0 cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n t\f0\lang1033\'f9y ch\f2\lang1066\u7881?nh tr\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889? c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh.\b0\par
\b\fs28 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\f2\lang1066\u7853?t kh\u7849?u\b0\fs22\par
M\u7885?i ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7873?u nghi ng\u7901? v\u7873? kh\u7843? n\f1\'e3ng b\f2\u7843?o m\u7853?t th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a h\u7885?. H\u7879? th\u7889?ng kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\f2\lang1066\u7847?n m\u7853?t kh\u7849?u n\f0\lang1033\'e0y cho ph\'e9p ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7879?n quy tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c m\f0\lang1033\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\f2\lang1066\u7847?n nh\u7853?p m\u7853?t kh\u7849?u c\u7911?a h\u7885?. Ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p b\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?p \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?a ch\u7881? email ho\u7863?c s\u7889? \f1\'f0i\f2\u7879?n tho\u7841?i. Ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? nh\u7853?n \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c m\u7897?t l\f0\lang1033\'e1 th\f1\u432? c\f0\'f3 li\'ean k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t m\u7897?t l\u7847?n ho\u7863?c m\f0\lang1033\'e3 \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p.\par
\b\f0\fs32\lang1033 3.\f2\lang1066 L\u7907?i \f0\lang1033\'edch c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a Auth0\b0\fs22\par
