\tab Quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n s\u7903? h\u7919?u: Vi\u7879?c \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c ph\f0\lang1033\'e2n lo\f2\lang1066\u7841?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 b\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? nh\u7845?t hay b\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? ba t\f0\lang1033\'f9y thu\f2\lang1066\u7897?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0o quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n s\u7903? h\u7919?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n ki\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng. C\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a b\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? nh\u7845?t \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c ki\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t b\f2\lang1066\u7903?i c\f0\lang1033\'f9ng m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t t\u7893? ch\u7913?c ho\u7863?c c\f0\lang1033\'e1 nh\'e2n s\f2\lang1066\u7903? h\u7919?u mi\u7873?n Auth0. \u7912?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a b\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? ba cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p c\'e1c b\'ean ho\f2\lang1066\u7863?c \f1\'f0\f2\u7889?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\'ean ngo\'e0i truy c\f2\lang1066\u7853?p an to\f0\lang1033\'e0n v\'e0o c\'e1c t\'e0i nguy\'ean \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c b\u7843?o v\u7879? \f1\'f0\f2\u7857?ng sau API c\u7911?a b\u7841?n. \f1\'d0\f2\u7875? t\f0\lang1033\'ecm hi\f2\lang1066\u7875?u th\f0\lang1033\'eam, h\'e3y \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7885?c \u7912?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a b\f0\lang1033\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? nh\u7845?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 b\'ean th\f2\lang1066\u7913? ba.\par
\b\f0\fs32\lang1033 2.\f2\lang1066 API Auth0\b0\fs22\par
Auth0 ti\u7871?t l\u7897? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c API sau \f1\'f0\f0\'e2y \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f2\lang1066\u7875?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng trong c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng c\u7911?a h\u7885?.\par
API x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c\par
API x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c hi\u7875?n th\u7883? ch\u7913?c n\f1\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?n d\u7841?ng cho Auth0 v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'e1c giao th\f2\lang1066\u7913?c nh\u7853?n d\u7841?ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c h\u7895? tr\u7907? (bao g\u7891?m OpenID Connect, OAuth v\f0\lang1033\'e0 SAML).\par
Th\'f4ng th\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?ng, b\u7841?n n\f0\lang1033\'ean s\f2\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng API n\f0\lang1033\'e0y th\'f4ng qua m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t trong c\f0\lang1033\'e1c SDK Auth0, ch\f2\lang1066\u7859?ng h\u7841?n nh\f1\u432? Auth0.js ho\f2\u7863?c m\u7897?t th\f1\u432? vi\f2\u7879?n nh\f1\u432? Kh\f0\lang1033\'f3a. Tuy nhi\'ean, n\f2\lang1066\u7871?u b\u7841?n \f1\'f0ang x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f2\lang1066\u7921?ng giao di\u7879?n ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh theo c\'e1ch th\f2\lang1066\u7911? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng, b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n s\u7869? c\u7847?n g\u7885?i tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p API x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c.\par
\b M\u7897?t s\u7889? nhi\u7879?m v\u7909? v\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f2\lang1066\u7909? bao g\u7891?m\b0 :\par
Nh\u7853?n m\f0\lang1033\'e3 th\'f4ng b\'e1o trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c\par
Y\f0\lang1033\'eau c\f2\lang1066\u7847?u h\u7891? s\f1\u417? c\f2\u7911?a ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng b\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng M\f0\lang1033\'e3 truy c\f2\lang1066\u7853?p\par
Trao \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i m\f0\lang1033\'e3 l\'e0m m\f2\lang1066\u7899?i \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? l\u7845?y m\f0\lang1033\'e3 truy c\f2\lang1066\u7853?p m\u7899?i\par
Y\f0\lang1033\'eau c\f2\lang1066\u7847?u th\u7917? th\f0\lang1033\'e1ch \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0a y\f2\u7871?u t\u7889? (MFA)\par
Tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh kh\'e1m ph\'e1 API\par
T\'ecm hi\f2\lang1066\u7875?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 kh\'e1m ph\'e1 c\'e1c y\'eau c\f2\lang1066\u7847?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\f2\lang1066\u7843?n h\u7891?i cho \f1\'f0i\f2\u7875?m cu\u7889?i API x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c Auth0 trong tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh duy\f2\lang1066\u7879?t c\u7911?a b\u7841?n v\u7899?i Tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh kh\'e1m ph\'e1 API x\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c.\par
