\b\fs28 API qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd\b0\fs22\par
API qu\f2\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd cho ph\'e9p b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd t\'e0i kho\f2\lang1066\u7843?n Auth0 c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh theo l\f2\lang1066\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh, v\'ec v\f2\lang1066\u7853?y b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? t\u7921? \f1\'f0\f2\u7897?ng c\u7845?u h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh m\'f4i tr\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?ng c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh. H\f2\lang1066\u7847?u h\u7871?t c\f0\lang1033\'e1c t\'e1c v\f2\lang1066\u7909? b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n trong B\u7843?ng \f1\'f0i\f2\u7873?u khi\u7875?n qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd Auth0 c\f1\u361?ng c\f0\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n theo ch\f1\u432?\u417?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh b\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch s\f2\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng API n\f0\lang1033\'e0y.\par
\b M\f2\lang1066\u7897?t s\u7889? nhi\u7879?m v\u7909? v\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f2\lang1066\u7909? bao g\u7891?m:\b0\par
\f1\'d0\'e3ng k\f0\lang1033\'fd c\'e1c \f2\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 API c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a b\u7841?n v\u7899?i Auth0\par
Thi\u7871?t l\u7853?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t n\u7889?i m\f0\lang1033\'e0 ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c\par
Qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng\par
Li\'ean k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t t\f0\lang1033\'e0i kho\f2\lang1066\u7843?n ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng\par
Ph\'e2n trang\par
\f1\'d0\f2\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i thu\f0\lang1033\'ea \f1\'d0\f0\'e1m m\'e2y c\'f4ng c\f2\lang1066\u7897?ng, \f1\'f0i\f2\u7875?m cu\u7889?i API qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd tr\f2\lang1066\u7843? v\u7873? t\u7889?i \f1\'f0a 50 k\f2\u7871?t qu\u7843? cho m\u7895?i ph\u7843?n h\u7891?i. Khi c\f0\lang1033\'f3 nhi\f2\lang1066\u7873?u k\u7871?t qu\u7843? h\f1\u417?n s\f2\u7889? k\u7871?t qu\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c tr\u7843? l\u7841?i trong m\u7897?t ph\u7843?n h\u7891?i, h\f0\lang1033\'e3y bao g\f2\lang1066\u7891?m trang v\f0\lang1033\'e0 tham s\f2\lang1066\u7889? per_page trong y\f0\lang1033\'eau c\f2\lang1066\u7847?u c\u7911?a b\u7841?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? l\u7845?y th\f0\lang1033\'eam k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t qu\u7843?.\par
