\b\fs28 Tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh kh\'e1m ph\'e1 API\b0\fs22\par
T\'ecm hi\f2\lang1066\u7875?u v\u7873? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f2\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng API qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd Auth0 trong tr\'ecnh duy\f2\lang1066\u7879?t c\u7911?a b\u7841?n v\u7899?i Tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh kh\'e1m ph\'e1 API qu\f2\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd.\par
