\b\fs32 4.Qu\f2\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd danh t\'ednh ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng v\'e0 th\'f4ng tin h\f2\lang1066\u7891? s\f1\u417?\b0\fs22\par
C\f0\lang1033\'f3 m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t s\u7889? c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917?a \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin trong h\f2\lang1066\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng ho\f2\lang1066\u7863?c M\f0\lang1033\'e3 th\'f4ng b\'e1o ID.\par
Ph\f2\lang1066\u7841?m vi: C\f0\lang1033\'e1c lu\f2\lang1066\u7891?ng x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c h\u7895? tr\u7907? b\u7903?i Auth0 bao g\u7891?m m\u7897?t tham s\u7889? t\f0\lang1033\'f9y ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n cho ph\f0\lang1033\'e9p b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh ph\u7841?m vi. \f1\'d0i\f2\u7873?u n\f0\lang1033\'e0y ki\f2\lang1066\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t th\'f4ng tin h\f2\lang1066\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng (x\'e1c nh\f2\lang1066\u7853?n quy\u7873?n s\u7903? h\u7919?u) \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c bao g\u7891?m trong M\f0\lang1033\'e3 th\'f4ng b\'e1o ID (JWT).\par
Trang t\f2\lang1066\u7893?ng quan qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd: Tr\'ean trang t\f2\lang1066\u7893?ng quan, qu\u7843?n tr\u7883? vi\f0\lang1033\'ean c\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? ch\u7881?nh s\u7917?a th\u7911? c\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'e1c ph\f2\lang1066\u7847?n c\u7911?a h\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng cho m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\f2\lang1066\u7909? th\u7875?. C\f1\u417? ch\f2\u7871? n\f0\lang1033\'e0y c\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? thay \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i ph\u7847?n user_metadata v\f0\lang1033\'e0 app_metadata c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a h\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng.\par
API qu\f2\lang1066\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd: Cung c\f2\lang1066\u7845?p quy\u7873?n truy c\u7853?p \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? \f1\'f0\f2\u7885?c, c\u7853?p nh\u7853?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 x\'f3a h\f2\lang1066\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c l\f1\u432?u tr\f2\u7919? trong c\f1\u417? s\f2\u7903? d\u7919? li\u7879?u Auth0.\par
T\u7853?p l\u7879?nh c\f1\u417? s\f2\u7903? d\u7919? li\u7879?u t\f0\lang1033\'f9y ch\f2\lang1066\u7881?nh: N\u7871?u c\f1\u417? s\f2\u7903? d\u7919? li\u7879?u t\f0\lang1033\'f9y ch\f2\lang1066\u7881?nh \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0m k\f2\lang1066\u7871?t n\u7889?i, b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? vi\u7871?t t\u7853?p l\u7879?nh \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? tri\u7875?n khai c\f0\lang1033\'e1c s\f2\lang1066\u7921? ki\u7879?n v\f0\lang1033\'f2ng \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7901?i nh\f1\u432? t\f2\u7841?o, \f1\'f0\'e3ng nh\f2\u7853?p, x\f0\lang1033\'e1c minh, x\'f3a v\'e0 thay \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7893?i m\u7853?t kh\u7849?u. Auth0 cung c\u7845?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c m\f2\lang1066\u7851?u cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c t\f2\lang1066\u7853?p l\u7879?nh n\f0\lang1033\'e0y m\'e0 b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? s\u7917?a \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i cho c\f1\u417? s\f2\u7903? d\u7919? li\u7879?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c \f1\'f0\f2\u7891? c\u7909? th\u7875?.\par
Quy t\u7855?c: Quy t\u7855?c th\u7921?c thi sau khi ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\f0\'e3 \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c. S\u7917? d\u7909?ng Quy t\u7855?c \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? t\f1\'e3ng c\u432?\f2\u7901?ng h\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng trong qu\'e1 tr\'ecnh giao d\f2\lang1066\u7883?ch x\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\f2\lang1066\u7921?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\'f9y ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n duy tr\f0\lang1033\'ec nh\f2\lang1066\u7919?ng thay \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i \f1\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 tr\f2\lang1066\u7903? l\u7841?i Auth0.\par
