\b\f0\fs32\lang1033 5.\f2\lang1066 Ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng\b0\fs22\par
B\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng b\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng Trang t\u7893?ng quan Auth0 ho\u7863?c API qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd. C\'e1c quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng v\u7899?i b\u7897? t\f0\lang1033\'ednh n\f1\'e3ng API Authorization Core.\par
Vi\f2\lang1066\u7879?c th\f0\lang1033\'eam quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n tr\u7921?c ti\u7871?p cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng l\'e0m m\f2\lang1066\u7845?t \f1\'f0i l\f2\u7907?i \f0\lang1033\'edch c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a ki\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t truy c\f2\lang1066\u7853?p d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean vai tr\'f2 (RBAC) v\'e0 th\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?ng kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7907?c khuy\u7871?n ngh\u7883?.\par
\f1\'d0i\f2\u7873?u ki\u7879?n ti\f0\lang1033\'ean quy\f2\lang1066\u7871?t\par
\f1\'d0\f2\u7875? ki\u7875?m so\f0\lang1033\'e1t truy c\f2\lang1066\u7853?p d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean vai tr\'f2 (RBAC) ho\f2\lang1066\u7841?t \f1\'f0\f2\u7897?ng b\f0\lang1033\'ecnh th\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?ng, b\u7841?n ph\u7843?i b\u7853?t n\f0\lang1033\'f3 cho API c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh b\f2\lang1066\u7857?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch s\f2\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng B\u7843?ng \f1\'f0i\f2\u7873?u khi\u7875?n ho\u7863?c API qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd. Ch\f2\lang1066\u7913?c n\f1\'e3ng C\f2\u7889?t l\f0\lang1033\'f5i \f2\lang1066\u7911?y quy\u7873?n kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\f2\lang1066\u7899?i Ti\u7879?n \f0\lang1033\'edch m\f2\lang1066\u7903? r\u7897?ng \u7911?y quy\u7873?n. \f1\'d0\f2\u7875? so s\f0\lang1033\'e1nh, h\'e3y \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7885?c Ph\u7847?n m\u7903? r\u7897?ng \u7911?y quy\u7873?n so v\u7899?i Ph\u7847?n m\u7903? r\u7897?ng \u7911?y quy\u7873?n.\par
Thi\u7871?t l\u7853?p m\u7897?t API trong Trang t\u7893?ng quan.\par
Quy\u7873?n \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c ch\u7885?n t\u7915? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c gi\'e1 tr\f2\lang1066\u7883? \f1\'f0\u432?\f2\u7907?c x\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7883?nh tr\f1\u432?\f2\u7899?c. N\u7871?u danh s\f0\lang1033\'e1ch vai tr\'f2 c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a b\u7841?n tr\u7889?ng, h\f0\lang1033\'e3y \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7843?m b\u7843?o b\u7841?n th\f0\lang1033\'eam quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n cho API c\u7911?a m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh.\par
\b b\f2\lang1066\u7843?ng \f1\'f0i\f2\u7873?u khi\u7875?n\b0\par
C\f0\lang1033\'f3 hai c\'e1ch \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? g\f0\lang1033\'e1n quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng. B\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? ch\u7885?n ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng t\f2\lang1066\u7915? danh s\f0\lang1033\'e1ch Ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng v\'e0 sau \f1\'f0\f0\'f3 ch\f2\lang1066\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n ho\u7863?c b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? truy c\u7853?p trang Chi ti\u7871?t ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng (h\f2\lang1066\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng) cho m\f2\lang1066\u7897?t ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng c\'e1 nh\'e2n v\'e0 ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n quy\u7873?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh trong tab Quy\u7873?n.\par
Ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n trong danh s\f0\lang1033\'e1ch ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng\par
\f1\'d0i t\f2\lang1066\u7899?i Trang t\u7893?ng quan> Qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng> Ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng.\par
B\f2\lang1066\u7845?m ... b\f0\lang1033\'ean c\f2\lang1066\u7841?nh ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n s\u7917?a \f1\'f0\f2\u7893?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n G\f0\lang1033\'e1n quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n.\par
Ch\u7885?n API m\f0\lang1033\'e0 b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n, sau \f1\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n quy\u7873?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng v\'e0 nh\f2\lang1066\u7845?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o Th\'eam quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n.\par
Ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n trong h\u7891? s\f1\u417? ng\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng\par
B\f2\lang1066\u7841?n c\f1\u361?ng c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f2\lang1066\u7875? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng t\f2\lang1066\u7915? trang h\u7891? s\f1\u417? c\f0\lang1033\'e1 nh\'e2n c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a h\u7885?.\par
\f1\'d0i t\f2\u7899?i Trang t\u7893?ng quan> Qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng> Ng\f1\u432?\f2\lang1066\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng v\'e0 nh\f2\lang1066\u7845?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o t\'ean c\f2\lang1066\u7911?a ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng \f1\'f0\f2\lang1066\u7875? xem.\par
Nh\u7845?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o tab Quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\f2\lang1066\u7845?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o Ch\f2\lang1066\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh Quy\u7873?n.\par
Ch\u7885?n API m\f0\lang1033\'e0 b\f2\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh quy\u7873?n, sau \f1\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 ch\f2\lang1066\u7885?n quy\u7873?n \f1\'f0\f2\u7875? ch\u7881? \f1\'f0\f2\u7883?nh cho ng\f1\u432?\f2\u7901?i d\f0\lang1033\'f9ng v\'e0 nh\f2\lang1066\u7845?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0o Th\'eam quy\f2\lang1066\u7873?n.\par
